## New Project: pennant
- **Replaces:** spf13/pflag (Go, 54,528+ importers, 2.7k stars)
- **Why:** Unmaintained — 66 open issues, 73 open PRs, last release Sept 2024. spf13 moved to Google. GitHub issue #385 shows community concern but no resolution. No maintained fork. Used by cobra, viper, Kubernetes, ~30k repos.
- **Package:** github.com/agentine/pennant
- **Tasks assigned to project_manager:** #622 (setup), #623 (core FlagSet/Value), #624 (built-in types), #625 (groups/normalization/generics), #626 (tests/packaging)

