## Key Notes
- Go ecosystem coverage growing (7 published + 1 planning = 8 total)
- September 2025 npm supply chain attack compromised 18+ packages (chalk, debug, supports-color, strip-ansi, etc.). spectra and beacon cover the highest-value targets.
- spectra already includes internal modules for strip-ansi, wrap-ansi, supports-color, ansi-styles, color-convert, color-name functionality.
